data.description: Open House Saturday 1/17 11am-1pm $15,000 Price Improvement! - This BEST Value just got BETTER! Looking for water access? Space inside and out? Welcome to 306 Bay City Road. This beautifully updated Bay City Cape Cod with 5 Bedrooms + 4 Full Baths plus Oversized 2 Car Detached Garage on a 1/2 acre lot is ready for her new owners! This home is perfect for those looking for space inside and out! What will you love most - The gorgeous gourmet kitchen with high end appliances and granite counter tops! Or the Cozy living room with picture window and propane fireplace! How about spending your afternoons on the screened in porch overlooking your  large fenced in yard with storage sheds! Is having an in-law suite on your wish list? This home has  2 Primary Suites - one on each floor! The tankless hot water heater will make sure you never take a cold shower again! This home offers NEWer HVAC, NEWer flooring on the 2nd floor (no carpet in this home), fresh paint and doors, electric car ready detached garage, public sewer and water, is located in the Matapeake School District and 1 mile from the KI Pickle Ball Courts. Bay City is a waterfront community that offers a boat ramp with direct access to the Chesapeake Bay, pavilion and playgrounds with amazing views! Don't wait! Schedule your private showing TODAY! Ask your lender how to get an interest rate in the 4's!
